Created `Infrastructure/FileSystemWrapper.cs` — a decorator that implements `IFileSystem` by forwarding every property to an inner instance.

**Usage:**

```csharp
// Production DI registration
services.AddSingleton<IFileSystem>(new FileSystemWrapper(new FileSystem()));

// Tests — pass MockFileSystem directly (no wrapper needed)
var svc = new DataService(new MockFileSystem());
```

You can override any property in the wrapper to add logging, caching, or path normalization without touching consumer code.
